pageContext.claim: “The Fake News Media keeps saying we haven't built any NEW WALL. Below is a section just completed on the Border. Anti-climbing feature included. Very high, strong and beautiful! Also, many miles already renovated and in service!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump tweeted a photo of bollard fencing, a design mandated by Congress which refused to allow him funds to use the concrete designs he had touted during a trip to California.
